<script>

    var RatingsWidget = (function () {
        var allowedLocations = [
            'Maryland, United States',
            'Oberösterreich, Austria'
        ]
        var allowedLogTypeSrcs = [
            '/images/logtypes/48/2.png', // Found It
            '/images/logtypes/48/3.png'  //DNF
        ]
        var ratings = [
            'condition-rating',
            'fun-rating',
            'overall-rating'
        ]
        var activeClass = 'active';
        var hiddenClass = 'hidden';
        var ratingWidget = document.getElementById('cache-rating-widget');
        var closeCTA = document.getElementById('rating-widget-close-cta');
        var submitButton = document.getElementById('submit-rating-widget');
        var textArea = document.getElementById('ctl00_ContentBody_CacheRatingWidget_ratingTextarea');
        var textAreaPlaceholderEle = document.getElementById('cache-rating-textarea-placeholder');
        var errorMessage = document.getElementById('ratings-error-message');
        var successMessageWrapper = document.getElementById('cache-rating-widget-success-message');
        var successMessageCloseCTA = document.getElementById('rating-widget-success-close-cta');

        _showWidget = function () {
            ratingWidget.classList.remove(hiddenClass);
        }

        _hideWidget = function () {
            ratingWidget.classList.add(hiddenClass);
        }

        _showSuccessMessage = function () {
            successMessageWrapper.classList.remove(hiddenClass)
        }

        _hideSuccessMessage = function () {
            successMessageWrapper.classList.add(hiddenClass)
        }

        _getRatingValueByName = function (inputName) {
            var ratingInput = document.querySelector('input[name="' + inputName + '"]:checked')
            if (ratingInput === null) {
                return null;
            }
            return ratingInput.value;
        }

        _allRatingsAreSelected = function() {
            for (var i = 0; i < ratings.length; i++) {
                var ratingValue = _getRatingValueByName(ratings[i])
                if (ratingValue === null) {
                    return false;
                }
            }
            return true;
        }

        _showRatingsErrorMessage = function () {
            errorMessage.classList.add(activeClass);
        }

        _sendRatings = function () {
            var ratingsSendObject = {
                logId: _getLogId(),
                overallRating : _getRatingValueByName('overall-rating'),
                healthRating :  _getRatingValueByName('condition-rating'),
                funRating :  _getRatingValueByName('fun-rating'),
                message : textArea.value
            }

            // Create Request
            var postURL = '../seek/cache_details.aspx/SubmitContentSurvey';
            var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
            xhr.open('POST', postURL, true);
            xhr.setRequestHeader("Content-Type", "application/json;charset=UTF-8");

            xhr.send(JSON.stringify(ratingsSendObject));

            //console.log('ratingsSendObject:')
            //console.log(ratingsSendObject)
            // Hide Widget, show success message
            _hideWidget();
            _showSuccessMessage();
        }

        _initEvents = function () {
            //Widget - Submit Button
            submitButton.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                if (_allRatingsAreSelected()) {
                    _sendRatings();
                } else {
                    _showRatingsErrorMessage();
                }
            });
            //Widget - Close Button
            closeCTA.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                _hideWidget();
            })
            // Success Message - Close Button
            successMessageCloseCTA.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                _hideSuccessMessage();
            })
        }

        _isInArray = function (val, a) {
            for (var i = 0; i < a.length; i++) {
                if (val === a[i])
                    return true;
            }
            return false;
        }

        _doesContainStringFromArray = function (s, a) {
            for (var i = 0; i < a.length; i++) {
                if (s.indexOf(a[i]) !== -1)
                    return true;
            }
            return false;
        }

        _getLogId = function () {
            var logIdEleId = 'ctl00_ContentBanner_uxNewLogId';
            var logIdEle = document.getElementById(logIdEleId);
            if (logIdEle === null)
                return null
            return logIdEle.value;
            /*
            var url = location.href;
            var paramKey = 'luid';
            var hasLuidInURL = url.indexOf(paramKey + '=') !== -1
            if (!hasLuidInURL)
                return null;
            var splitUrl = url.split(paramKey + '=')
            var secondHalf = splitUrl[1]
            if (secondHalf.indexOf('&') !== -1)
                secondHalf = secondHalf.split('&')[0]
            return secondHalf;
            */
        }

        _isSupposedToShow = function () {
            // Is Auth
            var logCTAId = 'ctl00_ContentBody_GeoNav_logButton';
            var logCTAEle = document.getElementById('logCTAId');
            var isAuth = logCTAEle === null
            // console.log('isAuth?: ' + isAuth)
            if (!isAuth)
                return false;

            // Has Logged / DNF'd Cache
            var logTypeImageId = 'ctl00_ContentBody_GeoNav_logTypeImage';
            var logTypeImageEle = document.getElementById(logTypeImageId);
            // console.log('logImageExists?: ' + !(logTypeImageEle === null))
            if (logTypeImageEle === null)
                return false;
            var logTypeImageSrc = logTypeImageEle.getAttribute('src');
            var hasLoggedCache = _isInArray(logTypeImageSrc, allowedLogTypeSrcs);
            // console.log('hasLoggedCache2?: ' + hasLoggedCache)
            if (!hasLoggedCache)
                return false;

            // Location
            var cacheLocationParentId = 'ctl00_ContentBody_Location';
            var cacheLocationParent = document.getElementById(cacheLocationParentId);
            if (cacheLocationParent === null)
                return false;
            var cacheLocationMixedString = cacheLocationParent.textContent;
            var isAllowedLocation = _doesContainStringFromArray(cacheLocationMixedString, allowedLocations);
            // console.log('isAllowedLoc?: ' + isAllowedLocation);
            if (!isAllowedLocation)
                return false;

            // Has Just Posted Log
            if (_getLogId() === null)
                return false;

            return true;
        }

        _setUpWidget = function () {
            // Steal Title from page
            var widgetTitleId = 'rating-widget-cache-name';
            var widgetTitleEle = document.getElementById('rating-widget-cache-name');
            var cachePageTitleId = 'ctl00_ContentBody_CacheName';
            var cachePageTitleEle = document.getElementById(cachePageTitleId);
            if (cachePageTitleEle !== null)
                widgetTitleEle.textContent = cachePageTitleEle.textContent

            // Set Placeholder for Textarea
            textArea.setAttribute('placeholder', textAreaPlaceholderEle.textContent);

            // Show widget once loaded
            _showWidget();
        }

        return {
            init: function () {
                if (_isSupposedToShow()) {
                    // Set Up Widget Events
                    _initEvents();
                    // Show Widget
                    _setUpWidget();
                }
            }
        }
    })();

    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
        RatingsWidget.init();
    });

</script>

        <br />
        <div class="UserSuppliedContent">
            
            <span id="ctl00_ContentBody_LongDescription"><center><img src="http://img.geocaching.com/cache/9959bd62-c91f-45f5-947c-3e4aaa1e98f8.jpg" width="134" height="226" alt="krizek" /></center>
<p align="center" style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="6"><b>Geocaching jinak</b></font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>S geocachingem to jde posledni dobou z kopce.</i></font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>- V mediich se objevuje stale casteji.</i></font><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>- Zkousi se mu venovat vic a vic lidi.</i></font><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>- Nove kese rostou jak houby po desti, a hodne z nich nestoji za vic nez za bod.</i></font><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>- Mnozi se pokusy o publikovani kontroverznich kesi s pozadavkem na precedent.</i></font><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>- Ignore listy se plni mysterkami typu: na co autor myslel pri kodovani souradnic.</i></font><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>- Stare (kvalitni) kese se ztraceji, ci byvaji vymudleny.</i></font><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>- Coiny a TB se ztraceji spolu s kesemi, nebo jsou z nich cilene vybirany.</i></font><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>- A tak dale......doplnte sami</i></font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><b>A prave temto ztracenym sigitemum je urcena tato cache. (TB/GC hrbitov)</b></font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">Sem muzete pomoci "WN" umistit svuj ztraceny Coin ci TB.</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">Ti, co si ji budou chtit najit a zalogovat "Found It", musi zvladnout nasledujici ukol:</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>Cesky jazyk obsahuje asi 190 tisíc slov (Slovnik spisovneho jazyka ceskeho 1989). Ale jenom jedno se jinak pise a jinak cte. Na rozdil treba od anglickeho jazyka, kde se snad vsechna slova jinak pisi a jinak ctou.</i></font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><i>Toto slovo najdete a prevedte ho do Morseovy abecedy (tecky, carky) .</i></font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">Cache najdete na souradnicich:<br /></font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4"><br /></font></p>
<font size="4"><font size="6"><b>N 49° 0A.BCD<br />
E 017° 3E.FGH</b></font></font>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">Kde:</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">A = pocet vsech znaku v prvnim pismenu</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">B = pocet vsech znaku v druhem, ctvrtem a poslednim pismenu</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">C = pocet carek v prvnim pismenu</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">D = pocet tecek ve druhem a predposlednim pismenu</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">E = pocet vsech znaku ve tretim a predposlednim pismenu</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">F = pocet carek v prvnim a poslednim pismenu</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">G = B</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">H = pocet tecek ve tretim a poslednim pismenu</font></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><br /></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0cm;"><font size="4">Schranka je micro zamerne.<br /></font></p>
<center><font size="4">Souradnice si overte zde.</font></center>
<center><a href="http://geocheck.org/geo_inputchkcoord.php?gid=627973776474dc6-ee58-411c-9a42-ba09256d4f72"><img src="http://geocheck.org/geocheck_small.php?gid=627973776474dc6-ee58-411c-9a42-ba09256d4f72" title="Zkontrolujte Vaše řešení" border="0" /></a></center></span>

        function appendUpvotesToLogs(logIds) {
            $.ajax({
                type: "GET",
                url: "/account/oauth/token",
                success: function (result) {
                    $.ajax({
                        type: "GET",
                        url: "/api/proxy/web/v1/Geocaches/logs/upvote",
                        dataType: 'json',
                        headers: {
                            "Authorization": "Bearer " + result.access_token
                        },
                        data: {
                            geocacheLogIds: logIds.join(',')
                        },
                        success: function (data) {
                            for (var i = 0; i < logIds.length; i++) {
                                var key = logIds[i];
                                var upvoteInfo = data[key];
                                var $greatStory = $('.l-' + key + ' .great-story-btn');
                                var $helpful = $('.l-' + key + ' .helpful-btn');

                                formatUpvoteButton(
                                    $greatStory,
                                    upvoteInfo.greatStory.upvotedByUser,
                                    upvoteInfo.greatStory.count,
                                    1);

                                formatUpvoteButton(
                                    $helpful,
                                    upvoteInfo.helpful.upvotedByUser,
                                    upvoteInfo.helpful.count,
                                    2);
                            }

                            $('.upvotes').show();
                        }
                    });
                }
            });
        }

        function formatUpvoteButton(
            $upvoteBtn,
            upvotedByUser,
            upvoteCount,
            upvoteType) {
            if ($upvoteBtn) {
                if (upvotedByUser) {
                    $upvoteBtn.data('upvoted', true);
                    $upvoteBtn.addClass('upvoted');
                } else {
                    $upvoteBtn.data('upvoted', false);
                    $upvoteBtn.removeClass('upvoted');
                }

                var txt = '';
                if (upvoteType === 1) {
                    txt = "Great story";
                } else if (upvoteType === 2) {
                    txt = "Helpful";
                }

                if (upvoteCount > 0) {
                    txt += ' (' + upvoteCount + ')';
                }

                $upvoteBtn.find('span').text(txt);
            }
        }

        function upvoteLog(el, upvoteTypeId, logId) {
            var upvoteTypeId = el.data('upvote-type');
            var logId = el.data('log-id');
            var isRemove = el.data('upvoted');

            var upvoteType = upvoteTypeId === 1 ? "GreatStory" : "Helpful";
            var callType = "POST";

            if (isRemove) {
                callType = "DELETE";
            }

            el.data('upvoted', !isRemove);

            $('.upvotes .loading-' + logId).removeClass('hide');

            ga('send', 'event', 'Geocache Log Upvotes', isRemove ? "Removed upvote" : "Added upvote", upvoteType);

                        $('#lblSolutionInputError').text("Sorry unable to parse the coordinates you entered.");

                    }

                    if (hasError) {
                        var solutionResponse = $('#lblSolutionResponse');
                        solutionResponse.removeClass("solution-error");
                        solutionResponse.text("");
                        return false;
                    }

                    var recaptcha = "";

                        success: function (result) {

                            if (response.Success == false) {
                                textResult.addClass("solution-error");

                                if (!response.Verified) {
                                    textResult.text("Recaptcha validation failed.");
                                    $('#recaptcha-br').show();
                                    $('.g-recaptcha').show();
                                } else if (!response.FinalCoordsListed) {
